0long-term%20relationship%20didn't%20feel%20quite%20as%20cute.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20felt%20like%20I'd%20failed%20in%20life%2C%20with%20no%20tangible%20assets%20%E2%80%94%20or%20offspring%20%E2%80%94%20to%20my%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMoving%20back%20in%20with%20my%20parents%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20an%20overgrown%20teenager%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20that%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhappy-moved-back-in-with-my-parents-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoving%20back%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20naturally%20regressed%20to%20my%20teenage%20state.%20I%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20in%20my%20bedroom%2C%20snapped%20over%20questions%20about%20where%20I%20was%20going%2C%20and%20became%20disheartened%20when%20my%20millennial%20TV%20tastes%20were%20greeted%20with%20loaded%20sighs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20I%20was%20grateful%20for%20the%20more-than-generous%20family%20rate%20applied%20to%20my%20rent%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20lost%20a%20part%20of%20my%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fcost-of-living-crisis-mortgage-costs-britain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoaring%20costs%20of%20living%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20England%2C%20renting%20solo%20was%20out%20of%20the%20question%20for%20me%20as%20a%20single%20freelancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ons.gov.uk%2Feconomy%2Finflationandpriceindices%2Fbulletins%2Fprivaterentandhousepricesuk%2Fmarch2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOffice%20of%20National%20Statistics%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ONS)%2C%20average%20rental%20prices%20in%20England%20went%20up%20by%20nearly%209%25%20in%20the%20year%20leading%20up%20to%20February%202024%2C%20the%20highest%20rise%20in%20annual%20percentage%20since%20records%20began%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEventually%2C%20I%20began%20to%20consider%20house-sharing%20as%20an%20option%3C%2Fh2%3