C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Emily%20Tisshaw)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-offered-money-get-sober-drugs-alcohol-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20movie-theater%20veteran%20has%20launched%20a%20company%20that%20seeks%20to%20jolt%20the%20industry%20with%20AI%20and%20a%20new%20production%20studio%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223781%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20Fithian%20Chris%20Pizzello%20AP%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e3854f65bc79c6811342e18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222554%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20Fithian%2C%20former%20head%20of%20The%20National%20Association%20of%20Theatre%20Owners%20(NATO)%2C%20has%20launched%20The%20Fithian%20Group.%3Cp%3EChris%20Pizzello%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJohn%20Fithian%2C%20former%20head%20of%20NATO%2C%20formed%20The%20Fithian%20Group%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20improve%20movie%20production%2C%20distribution%2C%20and%20exhibition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20group%20is%20overseeing%20the%20building%20of%20a%20high-tech%20production%20studio%20in%20Europe%20and%20a%20data-infused%20direct%20distribution%20platform.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20platform%2C%20free%20of%20charge%20for%20theaters%20to%20use%2C%20provides%20data%20to%20guide%20decisions%20and%20reduce%20costs%20for%20theaters%20and%20filmmakers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20months%20after%20John%20Fithian%20retired%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20movie-theater-lobbyist%20group%20The%20National%20Association%20of%20Theatre%20Owners%20(NATO)%2C%20he%20was%20ready%20to%20get%20back%20to%20work.%20What%20he%20didn't%20realize%20was%20how%20much%20work%20needed%20to%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFithian%20worked%20for%20over%20twenty%20years%20fighting%20to%20keep%20movie%20theaters%20relevant%20in%20the%20constantly%20changing%20worlds%20of%20entertainment%20and%20technology.%20He%20was%20on%20the%20front%20lines%20for%20issues%20ranging%20from%20theaters%20changing%20to%20digital%20projection%2C%20to%20the%20advent%20of%20movies%20released%20via%20streaming%2C%20and%20theaters%20suddenly%20shuttering%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic.%20Now%2C%20Fithian%20is%20taking%20on%20perhaps%20his%20hardest%20challenge%20yet%3A%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20more%20movies%20to%20be%20made%20and%20theatrically%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20announced%20the%20formation%20of%20The%20Fithian%20Group%20in%20November%2C%20many%20thought%20Fithian%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20fellow%20former%20NATO%20execs%20Jackie%20Brenneman%20and%20Patrick%20Corcoran%2C%20who%20are%20founding%20partners%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20doing%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20work%20they%20did%20at%20the%20organization%3A%20being%20advocates%20for%20the%20theatrical%20experience.%20However%2C%20the%20three%20have%20much%20more%20ambitious%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20basic%20concept%20is%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20that%20we%20think%20we%20can%20help%20do%20to%20improve%20production%2C%20distribution%2C%20and%20exhibition%20of%20movies%2C%20things%20we%20could%20never%20really%20do%20at%20NATO%2C%26quot%3B%20Fithian%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20alongside%20Brenneman%20and%20Corcoran%20late%20last%20month.%20%26quot%3BAt%20NATO%2C%20you're%20representing%20the%20entire%20industry%2C%20so%20you%20can't%20take%20on%20competitive%20issues.%20I%20think%20all%20three%20of%20us%20enjoyed%20our%20careers%20there%2C%20but%20getting%20the%20band%20back%20together%20and%20focusing%20on%20business%20models%20and%20competitive%20things%20that%20we%20think%20can%20really%20improve%20the%20business%20is%20very%20exciting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFithian%20Group%20hopes%20to%20put%20a%20jolt%20in%20the%20industry%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20production%20studio%20in%20Europe%20and%20a%20direct%20distribution%20platform%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20just%20over%20four%20months%20old%2C%20The%20Fithian%20Group%20has%20found%20immediate%20interest%20from%20companies%20seeking%20assistance%20within%20the%20movie-theater%20business%20in%20everything%20from%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions%20to%20consultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20two%20projects%20in%20particular%20that%20Fithian%2C%20Brenneman%2C%20and%20Corcoran%20hope%20to%20be%20the%20main%20pillars%20of%20their%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20Fithian%2C%20Jackie%20Brenneman%2C%20Patrick%20Corcoran%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66069c613f923f7dab027916%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221534%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Fithian%20Group%20founding%20partners%20(L-R)%20John%20Fithian%2C%20Jackie%20Brenneman%2C%20and%20Patrick%20Corcoran.%3Cp%3EIah%20Bearden-Vrai%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20overseeing%20the%20building%20of%20a%20state-of-the-art%20production%20studio%20in%20Europe%20that%20can%20handle%20both%20virtual%20and%20traditional%20physical%20production.%20Fithian%20would%20not%20divulge%20where%20exactly%20the%20studio%20will%20be%20and%20would%20not%20name%20the%20partners%20involved%2C%20only%20saying%20they%20are%20European%20investors.%20But%20he%20said%20the%20plan%20is%20for%20the%20studio%20to%20rival%20that%20of%20UK's%20famed%20Pinewood%20Studio%20in%20its%20capabilities%20to%20take%20on%20any%20size%20of%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMajor%20studios%20are%20way%20below%20the%20level%20of%20releases%20that%20can%20sustain%20this%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20Fithian%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20get%20more%20of%20those%20mid-range%20and%20independent%20movies%20out%20to%20exhibitors%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20out%20to%20audiences.%20Having%20the%20latest%20and%20best%20in%20virtual%20production%20technologies%20will%20help%20the%20moviemaking%20process%20be%20cheaper.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20studio%20is%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20development%20with%20no%20projected%20construction%20start%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20major%20project%20is%20an%20AI-assisted%2C%20data-infused%20direct%20distribution%20platform%20that%20filmmakers%2C%20independent%20distributors%2C%20and%20theaters%20can%20use%20to%20get%20more%20movies%20screened%20in%20theaters%20at%20reduced%20costs.%20For%20decades%2C%20theaters%20%E2%80%94%20through%20bookers%20%E2%80%94%20have%20had%20an%20endless%20dance%20of%20negotiating%20with%20distributors%20and%20studios%20for%20titles%20to%20play%20in%20theaters%20with%20little%20more%20than%2C%20as%20Fithian%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20spreadsheets%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20phone%20calls.%26quot%3B%20This%20has%20caused%20the%20business%20to%20often%20rely%20heavily%20on%20relationships%20over%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20The%20Fithian%20Group%20is%20overseeing%2C%20which%20is%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20development%2C%20will%20update%20that%20process%20and%20provide%20both%20sides%20with%20more%20informed%20decision-making%20capabilities%2C%20the%20group%20believes.%20A%20theater%20can%20use%20specific%20data%20through%20the%20platform%20to%20show%20a%20distributor%20why%20a%20particular%20type%20of%20movie%20should%20be%20played%20in%20their%20house.%20A%20filmmaker%20or%20distributor%20can%20also%20use%20the%20platform%20to%20show%20data%20to%20a%20theater%20about%20why%20their%20movie%20should%20be%20played%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20distributor%20in%20the%20past%20would%20say%2C%20'We%20never%20book%20in%20that%20market%2C%20we%20never%20book%20that%20kind%20of%20theater%2C'%20but%20the%20theater%20now%20is%20going%20to%20have%20data%20showing%20this%20audience%20is%20here%20for%20this%20kind%20of%20movie.%20Book%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Corcoran%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20take%20away%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20gatekeepers%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20mystery%2C%20and%20open%20up%20and%20democratize%20the%20system%20using%20technology.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22alamo%20drafthouse%20AP%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F59bff7ff38d20d21008b76f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Fithian%20Group%20is%20looking%20to%20get%20more%20movies%20into%20theaters%20and%20satisfy%20more%20audiences.%20%3Cp%3EAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EMore%20data%20to%20better%20program%20for%20audiences%20would%20be%20a%20welcome%20tool%2C%20one%20movie%20theater%20executive%20says%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDylan%20Skolnick%2C%20the%20co-director%20of%20Cinema%20Arts%20Centre%2C%20an%20arthouse%20in%20Long%20Island%2C%20New%20York%2C%20said%20new%20releases%20in%20his%20theater%20haven't%20consistently%20filled%20his%20house%20the%20way%20they%20did%20pre-pandemic.%20Having%20more%20data%20that%20shows%20what%20titles%20work%20best%20in%20his%20market%20would%20be%20beneficial%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20draw%20on%20data%20to%20develop%20the%20audience%20of%20people%20who%20really%20want%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20Skolnick%20said%20when%20Business%20Insider%20told%20him%20about%20the%20platform%20The%20Fithian%20Group%20is%20developing.%20Skolnick%20is%20also%20the%20booker%20of%20his%20theater%20and%20said%20there's%20never%20much%20talk%20about%20data%20when%20having%20conversations%20with%20distributors.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20slice%20and%20dice%20the%20internal%20data%20we%20have%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20but%20they%20will%20presumably%20have%20a%20lot%20more%20data%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20more%20computing%20power%2C%20so%20it%20could%20be%20great%20to%20use%20that%20platform%20%E2%80%94%20if%20we%20can%20afford%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20said%20the%20upcoming%20platform%20will%20be%20available%20free%20of%20charge%20for%20movie%20theaters.%20A%20fee%20and%20percentage%20of%20the%20box%20office%20will%20be%20charged%20to%20filmmakers%20and%20distributors%20who%20use%20the%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFithian%2C%20Brenneman%2C%20and%20Corcoran%20said%20they%20believe%20the%20endeavors%20they%20are%20undertaking%20will%20put%20a%20jolt%20into%20the%20movie%20business%2C%20which%20since%20the%20pandemic%20has%20suffered%20from%20lackluster%20box%20office%2C%20fewer%20titles%20being%20released%2C%20and%20not%20enough%20variety%20in%20the%20kinds%20of%20movies%20being%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20just%20thinking%20about%20sustaining%20the%20business%20the%20way%20it%20is%20and%20just%20participating%20in%20helping%20companies%20achieve%20the%20status%20quo%20and%20breaking%20in%20and%20doing%20the%20things%20they%20have%20always%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Brenneman%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20at%20the%20dawn%20of%20a%20new%20age%20of%20cinema%20where%20it%20doesn't%20cost%20almost%20anything%20to%20distribute%20a%20film.%20So%20there's%20a%20promise%20of%20digital%20cinema%2C%20which%20is%20more%20movies%2C%20more%20flexibility%2C%20more%20understanding%20of%20our%20audiences%2C%20and%20we're%20just%20there%20right%20now.%20There's%20lots%20and%20lots%20of%20AI%20out%20there%20to%20really%20help%20target%20the%20right%20movies%20for%20the%20right%20audiences%2C%20and%20we%20think%20we%20can%20really%20work%20with%20companies%20and%20individuals%20to%20get%20more%20movies%20into%20the%20theaters%20and%20satisfy%20more%20audiences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffithian-group-is-building-movie-production-studio-direct-distribution-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712149201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66069adc3f923f7dab027906%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2