rline_625x300_18_December_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvistara-expects-to-resume-normal-operations-by-weekend-sources-5366997%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vistara%20expects%20to%20resume%20normal%20flight%20ops%20by%20the%20weekend%2C%20company%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20Wednesday%2C%20hours%20after%20CEO%20Vinod%20Kannan%20and%20senior%20members%20of%20his%20management%20team%20held%20a%20virtual%20town%20hall%20with%20striking%20pilots.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvistara-expects-to-resume-normal-operations-by-weekend-sources-5366997%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvistara-expects-to-resume-normal-operations-by-weekend-sources-5366997%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvistara-expects-to-resume-normal-operations-by-weekend-sources-5366997%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Real%20Life%20'Invisibility%20Shield'%20Can%20Make%20You%20Disappear%20In%20Plain%20Sight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20British%20startup%2C%20Invisibility%20Shield%20Co.%2C%20created%20something%20straight%20out%20of%20a%20'Harry%20Potter'%20film.%20The%20startup%20has%20made%20a%206-foot-tall%20%26quot%3BMegashield%26quot%3B%20sold%20for%20%24828%2C%20which%20they%20claim%20that%20it%20can%20make%20multiple%20people%20invisible.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F04%2F02%2Flifestyle%2Fwild-invisibility-shield-makes-you-disappear-in-plain-sight-turning-science-fiction-into-reality%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20made%20shields%20by%20using%20ultra-large%2C%20precision-engineered%20lens%20arrays%2C%20which%20form%20the%20face%20of%20each%20shield%20and%20redirect%20light%20that%20reflects%20off%20the%20person%20standing%20behind%20the%20shield%2C%20away%20from%20the%20observer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20innovative%20shields%20use%20clever%20lens%20design%20to%20bend%20light%20around%20an%20object.%20By%20strategically%20capturing%20background%20light%20and%20directing%20it%20towards%20the%20viewer%2C%20they%20create%20the%20illusion%20of%20whatever's%20behind%20them%20simply%20disappearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20not%20perfect%20invisibility.%20The%20technology%20creates%20a%20slight%20blur%2C%20like%20a%20hidden%20object%20behind%20a%20frosted%20glass%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20limitation%2C%20the%20shields%20offer%20some%20impressive%20features.%20They're%20waterproof%2C%20require%20no%20power%20source%2C%20and%20are%20even%20eco-friendly%2C%20built%20entirely%20from%20recyclable%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20possibilities%20are%20endless%20but%20most%20important%20of%20all%2C%20these%20shields%20are%20great%20fun.%20They're%20fun%20to%20play%20around%20with%20and%20exciting%20for%20us%20to%20make%2C%26quot%3B%20Invisibility%20Shield%20designer%20Tristan%20Thompson%20told%20South%20West%20News%20Service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20launched%20its%20product%20in%202022%20with%20a%203-foot-tall%20shield%20worth%20%24354%20and%20a%20smaller%20version%20standing%20at%208%20inches%20tall%20sold%20for%20%2454.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20crowdfunded%20on%20Kickstarter%20in%20hopes%20of%20%26quot%3Bturning%20science%20fiction%20into%20reality%26quot%3B%20in%202022%20and%20raised%20a%20%246%2C600%20goal%20expecting%20to%20ship%20customers%20by%20the%20end%20of%20that%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvisibility%20Shield%20Co.%20updated%20the%20Kickstarter%20funder%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20announce%20the%20updated%20product.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20version%20of%20the%20invisibility%20shield%20can%20hide%20multiple%20people%2C%20stand%20on%20its%20own%20and%20be%20packed%20down%20to%202.3%20inches%20of%20thickness%2C%20%26quot%3Ballowing%20people%20to%20easily%20take%20them%20anywhere%20they%20want%20to%20disappear%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20see%20how%20far%20we%20could%20push%20this%20technology.%20A%20real%20working%20invisibility%20shield%20that%20you%20can%20just%20roll%20up%20and%20sling%20over%20your%20shoulder%3F%20Two%20years%20ago%20nobody%20thought%20anyone%20could%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Thompson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712148300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ftn2s2j_invisibility-shield_625x300_03_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fscience-fiction-into-reality-real-life-invisibility-shield-hides-users-in-plain-sight-5367208%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20innovative%20shields%20use%20clever%20lens%20design%20to%20bend%20light%20around%20an%20object.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fscience-fiction-into-reality-real-life-invisibility-shield-hides-users-in-plain-sight-5367208%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fscience-fiction-into-reality-real-life-invisibility-shield-hides-users-in-plain-sight-5367208%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fscience-fiction-into-reality-real-life-invisibility-shield-hides-users-in-plain-sight-5367208%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Court%20asks%20NIA%20to%20verify%20Pragya%20Thakur's%20health%20condition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712148244000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109009095%2Cimgsize-1577233.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fhampering-trial-court-asks-nia-to-verify-pragya-thakurs-health-condition-submit-report%2Farticleshow%2F109008896.cms%22%2C%22s