ent%20of%20Pharmaceuticals%20annually%20revises%20the%20ceiling%20prices%20of%20scheduled%20medicines%20based%20on%20the%20Wholesale%20Price%20Index%20(WPI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheduled%20medicines%20included%20in%20the%20Schedule-I%20of%20the%20DPCO%2C%202013%20are%20essential.%20During%20the%20calendar%20year%202023%20over%20the%20corresponding%20period%20in%202022%2C%20the%20annual%20change%20in%20WPI%20with%20base%20year%202011-12%20was%20(%20)%200.00551%20per%20cent%20as%20per%20data%20published%20by%20the%20Department%20for%20Promotion%20of%20Industry%20and%20Internal%20Trade%20(DPIIT).%20Accordingly%2C%20the%20Authority%20in%20its%20meeting%20held%20on%2020.03.2024%20has%20approved%20the%20WPI%20increase%20%40%20(%20)%200.00551%20per%20cent%20for%20the%20scheduled%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceiling%20prices%20on%20923%20medicines%20are%20effective%20as%20of%20date.%20Based%20on%20the%20above-mentioned%20WPI%20factor%20of%20(%20)%200.00551%20per%20cent%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20change%20in%20the%20prevailing%20ceiling%20prices%20for%20782%20medicines%20and%20the%20existing%20ceiling%20prices%20will%20continue%20to%20prevail%20up%20to%20March%2031%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifty-four%20(54)%20medicines%20with%20ceiling%20prices%20ranging%20from%20Rs%2090%20to%20Rs%20261%20will%20have%20a%20miniscule%20increase%20of%20Rs.%200.01%20(one%20paisa).%20As%20the%20permissible%20price%20increase%20is%20miniscule%2C%20the%20companies%20may%20or%20may%20not%20avail%20of%20this%20increase.%20Thus%2C%20in%20the%20year%20FY%202024-25%2C%20there%20will%20be%20almost%20no%20change%20in%20the%20ceiling%20price%20of%20medicines%20based%20on%20WPI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WPI%20increase%20is%20the%20maximum%20increase%20permissible%20as%20per%20the%20DPCO%2C%202013%20and%20the%20manufacturers%20may%20or%20may%20not%20avail%20of%20this%20increase%2C%20keeping%20in%20view%20the%20market%20dynamics.%20The%20companies%20adjust%20their%20Maximum%20Retail%20Price%20(MRP)%20depending%20on%20the%20ceiling%20price%20of%20their%20medicines%2C%20as%20MRP%20(excluding%20GST)%20can%20be%20any%20price%20that%20is%20less%20than%20the%20ceiling%20price.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712148120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-10%2Fchemist-generic-pharmacy_650x400_41443706936.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freports-claiming-big-hike-in-medicine-prices-are-false-misleading-centre-5366244%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20dismissed%20the%20media%20reports%20claiming%20that%20medicine%20prices%20will%20witness%20a%20significant%20hike%20by%20up%20to%2012%20per%20cent%20from%20April%202024%20and%20called%20them%20false%2C%20misleading%20and%20malicious.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freports-claiming-big-hike-in-medicine-prices-are-false-misleading-centre-5366244%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freports-claiming-big-hike-in-medicine-prices-are-false-misleading-centre-5366244%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freports-claiming-big-hike-in-medicine-prices-are-false-misleading-centre-5366244%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20stock%20market%20could%20face%20a%20near-term%20correction%20of%20as%20much%20as%2012%25%20before%20continuing%20its%20bull%20rally%20this%20summer%2C%20BofA%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bull%20and%20bear%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6540fb0a96f7540cd06a0e93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFollowing%20a%20glut%20of%20IPOs%20in%202021%2C%20broader%20market%20and%20economic%20uncertainty%20has%20led%20to%20a%202022%20tech%20IPO%20hiatus.%3Cp%3EiStock%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20stock%20market%20correction%20of%20as%20much%20as%2012%25%20could%20be%20imminent%2C%20according%20to%20Bank%20of%20America.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bank%20laid%20out%20a%20stock%20market%20roadmap%20that%20includes%20a%20decline%20before%20a%20summer%20bull%20rally.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20not%20rule%20out%20an%20April-May%20pause%20ahead%20of%20a%20June-August%20summer%20rally%2C%26quot%3B%20Bank%20of%20America%20said.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20stocks%20have%20been%20on%20a%20tear%20so%20far%20this%20year%2C%20surging%20about%2010%25%20in%20what%20has%20become%20the%2014th%20best%20first-quarter%20return%20on%20record%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fbac-stock%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%3EBank%20of%20America.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20considering%20that%202024%20is%20a%20Presidential%20election%20year%2C%20stocks%20are%20likely%20due%20for%20a%20pause%20over%20the%20next%20two%20months%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-secular-bull-rally-sp500-target-bofa-2024-3%5C%22%3Ebefore%20a%20summer%20bull%20rally%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20technical%20strategist%20Stephen%20Suttmeier%20said%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuttmeier%20highlighted%20that%20April%20and%20May%20have%20historically%20been%20weak%20months%20for%20stocks%20during%20a%20Presidential%20election%20year%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20flat%20in%20April%20and%20down%201.1%25%20in%20May%2C%20on%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20this%20uninspiring%20seasonality%2C%20we%20would%20not%20rule%20out%20an%20April-May%20pause%20ahead%20of%20a%20June-August%20summer%20rally%2C%26quot%3B%20Suttmeier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%2059%20days%20without%20a%202%25%20pullback%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20YCharts%2C%20so%20a%20correction%20is%20likely%20overdue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20sell-off%20does%20materialize%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20Suttmeier%20highlighted%20the%20following%20support%20levels%20to%20watch%20on%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%3A%204%2C800%20and%204%2C600%2C%20which%20represents%20key%20breakout%20levels%20from%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20decline%20to%204%2C600%20on%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20represents%20potential%20downside%20of%2012%25%20from%20current%20levels%2C%20which%20would%20be%20a%20garden%20variety%20sell-off%20for%20investors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%204%2C800%20and%204%2C600%20area%20breakout%20points%20offer%20big%20supports%20for%20the%20rest%20of%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20Suttmeier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20does%20fall%20back%20down%20to%20the%204%2C600%20area%2C%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20bull%20rally%20is%20over%2C%20according%20to%20Suttmeier%2C%20who%20put%20out%20a%20long-term%20technical%20price%20objective%20of%206%2C150%2C%20representing%20potential%20upside%20of%2018%25%20from%20current%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20January%20breakout%20above%20the%204%2C800%20area%20does%20not%20rule%20out%206%2C150%2C%20which%20aligns%20with%20the%20catch-up%20trade%20potential%20for%20a%20secular%20bull%20market%20Presidential%20Cycle%20into%20yearend%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20Suttmeier%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bull%20rally%20gains%20could%20be%20even%20higher%20based%20off%20the%20current%20magnitude%20of%20the%20stock%20market's%20rally%20that%20began%20in%20October%202022%2C%20according%20to%20the%20note.%3C%2Fp