t%20Inside%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20In%20Front%20Of%20Chief%20Justice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20allegedly%20attempted%20to%20die%20by%20suicide%20inside%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20today%20by%20slitting%20his%20throat%20with%20a%20knife%20in%20front%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20Nilay%20Vipinchandra%20Anjaria%20in%20Court%20Hall%20One%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Srinivas%2C%20who%20is%20from%20Mysuru%2C%20handed%20over%20a%20file%20to%20the%20security%20staff%20at%20the%20entrance%20of%20Court%20Hall%20One%2C%20and%20before%20anyone%20could%20realise%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20he%20slit%20his%20throat%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20Anjaria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20personnel%20responded%20immediately%20and%20rushed%20him%20to%20Bowring%20Hospital%2C%20where%20he%20is%20now%20being%20treated%2C%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20why%20he%20took%20such%20an%20extreme%20step.%20He%20entered%20Court%20Hall%20One%20and%20slit%20his%20throat%20with%20a%20knife.%20Our%20security%20staff%20saw%20it%20happen%20and%20immediately%20rescued%20him.%20He%20has%20been%20hospitalised%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20No%20note%20was%20found%20at%20the%20spot%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20Anjaria%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20security%20lapse%20on%20the%20High%20Court%20premises%20and%20asked%20those%20in%20charge%20how%20the%20man%20could%20bring%20a%20sharp%20object%20inside.%20He%20also%20ordered%20the%20police%20to%20record%20findings%20and%20evidence%20from%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contents%20of%20the%20file%20that%20Srinivas%20gave%20the%20security%20staff%20are%20unknown%2C%20and%20the%20court%20said%20it%20would%20not%20check%20the%20documents%20since%20it%20was%20not%20presented%20to%20the%20court%20by%20a%20designated%20advocate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20also%20said%20that%20the%20authorities%20must%20not%20receive%20any%20document%20without%20the%20court's%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20are%20still%20trying%20to%20find%20out%20why%20the%20man%20attempt%20to%20die%20by%20suicide%20and%20are%20waiting%20to%20record%20his%20statement%20once%20he%20is%20declared%20fit%20by%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712147940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2F7nrvsosc_karnataka-high-court-650_625x300_22_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-slits-his-throat-inside-karnataka-high-court-in-front-of-chief-justice-5367035%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20allegedly%20attempted%20to%20die%20by%20suicide%20inside%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20today%20by%20slitting%20his%20throat%20with%20a%20knife%20in%20front%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20Nilay%20Vipinchandra%20Anjaria%20in%20Court%20Hall%20One%2C%20the%20police%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-slits-his-throat-inside-karnataka-high-court-in-front-of-chief-justice-5367035%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-slits-his-throat-inside-karnataka-high-court-in-front-of-chief-justice-5367035%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-slits-his-throat-inside-karnataka-high-court-in-front-of-chief-justice-5367035%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bharat%20Series%20Number%20Plate%3A%20Eligibility%2C%20Benefits%20And%20How%20To%20Apply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20India%20introduced%20the%20BH%20series%20number%20plate%20or%20Bharat%20Series%20registration%20number%20for%20non-transport%20vehicles%20in%202021%20across%20India.%20The%20aim%20behind%20launching%20this%20was%20to%20facilitate%20the%20free%20movement%20of%20personal%20vehicles%20across%20states%2FUnion%20Territories%20of%20India%20upon%20relocation.%20This%20means%20that%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Series%20number%20plate%2C%20vehicle%20owners%20don't%20need%20to%20re-register%20their%20vehicles%20when%20moving%20to%20a%20new%20state.%20The%20BH%20series%20registration%20plate%20comes%20with%20a%20range%20of%20benefits%2C%20however%2C%20it%20also%20comes%20with%20some%20criteria%20to%20be%20eligible%20to%20get%20one.%20Here's%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20BH%20service%20license%20plate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEligibility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BH%20series%20number%20plate%20is%20not%20available%20to%20everyone.%20You%20can%20only%20get%20the%20license%20plate%20if%20you%20are%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20working%20for%20the%20central%20or%20state%20government%2C%20banks%2C%20defence%2C%20administrative%20services%2C%20etc.%20For%20those%20in%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20employees%20of%20companies%20with%20offices%20in%20a%20minimum%20of%20four%20Union%20Territories%20or%20Indian%20States%20are%20eligible%20for%20getting%20BH%20numbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20vehicle%20registration%20facility%20under%20%26quot%3BBharat%20series%20(BH-series)%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20available%20on%20a%20voluntary%20basis%20to%20Defence%20personnel%2C%20employees%20of%20Central%20Government%2F%20State%20Governments%2F%20Central%2F%20State%20Public%20Sector%20Undertakings%20and%20private%20sector%20companies%2Forganizations%2C%20which%20have%20their%20offices%20in%20four%20or%20more%20States%2FUnion%20territories%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ministry%20for%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20apply%20for%20BH%20series%20number%20plate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20purchasing%20a%20new%20car%2C%20car%20owners%20should%20fill%20up%20Form%2060%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20number%20plate%20and%20also%20provide%20valid%20proof%20of%20employment%20and%20IDs%20online.%20These%20documents%20will%20be%20verified%20by%20State%20Government%20authorities%20before%20BH%20registration%20is%20assigned.%20The%20number%20for%20registration%20will%20be%20randomly%20assigned%20to%20every%20applicant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECost%20and%20duration%20of%20BH%20number%20plate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20vehicles%20registered%20with%20a%20BH%20series%20number%20plate%2C%20the%20motor%20vehicle%20tax%20will%20be%20levied%20for%20two%20years%20or%20in%20multiple%20of%20two.%20After%20completion%20of%20the%20fourteenth%20year%2C%20the%20motor%20vehicle%20tax%20shall%20be%20levied%20annually%20which%20shall%20be%20half%20of%20the%20amount%20that%20was%20being%20charged%20earlier%20for%20that%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20BH-registered%20vehicles%20are%20transferable%20to%20both%20BH-series%20eligible%20and%20non-eligible%20buyers.%20If%20you%20purchase%20or%20sell%20the%20BH%20series%2C%20the%20buyer%20has%20to%20re-register%20the%20vehicle%20in%20his%20or%20her%20RTO%20to%20obtain%20the%20regional%20registration%20number.%20The%20new%20owner%20will%20also%20have%20to%20pay%20the%20registration%20fee%20and%20applicable%20taxes%20based%20on%20the%20regulations%20of%20the%20state%20or%20union%20territory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20BH%20number%20plates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20number%20and%20alphabet%20on%20a%20BH%20series%20number%20plate%20signifies%20something%20different.%20The%20first%20two%20numbers%20on%20the%20license%20plate%20signify%20the%20year%20of%20registration.%20BH%20stands%20for%20Bharat.%20The%20next%20four%20digits%20are%20randomly%20generated%20by%20the%20computer.%20This%20is%20followed%20by%20two%20random%20alphabets%2C%20excluding%20I%20and%20O.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712147940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fa5jve578_traffic-generic_625x300_04_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbharat-series-number-plate-eligibility-benefits-and-how-to-apply-5367162%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BH%20series%20registration%20plate%20comes%20with%20a%20range%20of%20benefits%2C%20however%2C%20it%20also%20comes%20with%20some%20criteria%20to%20be%20eligible%20to%20get%20one.%20Here's%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20BH%20service%20license%20plate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbharat-series-number-plate-eligibility-benefits-and-how-to-apply-5367162%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbharat-series-number-plate-eligibility-benefits-and-how-to-apply-5367162%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fbharat-series-number-plate-eligibility-benefits-and-how-to-apply-5367162%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mayank%20Or%20Coetzee%3F%20Controversy%20Over%20IPL%202024's%20Fastest%20Ball%20-%20Explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mayank%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F115355-mayank-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMayank%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20impressed%20both%20experts%20as%20well%20as%20fans%20with%20his%20fiery%20pace%20and%20during%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants'%20IPL%202024%20match%20against%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%2C%20he%20claimed%20the%20distinction%20of%20bowling%20the%20fastest%20delivery%20of%20this%20year's%20competition%20at%20156.7%20kmph.%20However%2C%20the%20record%20came%20with%20a%20slight%20controversy%20as%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Mumbai%20Indians%20fast%20bowler%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gerald%20Coetzee%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112523-gerald-coetzee-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGerald%20Coetzee%3C%2Fa%3E%20grabbed%20headlines%20for%20allegedly%20bowling%20a%20157.4%20kmph%20delivery%20against%20Rajasthan%20Royals.%20While%20the%20news%20did%20do%20the%20rounds%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20official%20list%20shown%20by%20IPL%20during%20LSG's%20game%20did%20not%20feature%20Coetzee's%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayank%20had%20earlier%20claimed%20the%20record%20with%20a%20fiery%20156.7%20kmph%20delivery%20during%20the%20match%20against%20Punjab%20Kings%20and%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20IPL%20claimed%20that%20the%20youngster%20has%20bettered%20his%20own%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20another%20list%20that%20showed%20the%20fastest%20deliveries%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20competition%20and%20it%20was%20topped%20by%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shaun%20Tait%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F622-shaun-tait-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShaun%20Tait%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20157.7%20kmph%20effort.%20He%20was%20followed%20by%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Lockie%20Ferguson%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64149-lachlan-hammond-ferguson-playerprofile%5C%22%3ELockie%20Ferguson%3C%2Fa%3E%20(157.3kph)%20and%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad's%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Umran%20Malik%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F113473-umran-malik-playerprofile%5C%22%3EUmran%20Malik%3C%2Fa%3E%20(157kph)%20and%20Mayank%20currently%20in%20fourth%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ESPNCricinfo%2C%20the%20speedometer%20was%20at%20fault%20in%20reading%20Coetzee's%20speed%20during%20the%20RR%20match%20and%20the%20actual%20speed%20of%20the%20delivery%20was%20actually%20around%20141%20kmph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20three-wicket%20haul%20against%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%2C%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG)%20pacer%20Mayank%20Yadav%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Cameron%20Green%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F113340-cameron-green-playerprofile%5C%22%3ECameron%20Green%3C%2Fa%3E's%20dismissal%20was%20special%20to%20him%20among%20other%20wickets.%3Cbr%3E%5CnWithin%20just%20two%20matches%2C%20Mayank%20has%20gathered%20headlines%20for%20his%20sheer%20pace%2C%20touching%20bowling%20speeds%20of%20150%20kmph-plus%20consistently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20shared%20on%20IPL's%20official%20social%20media%20handle%2C%20Mayank%20said%20that%20the%20over%20where%20he%20dismissed%20Green%20was%20very%20aggressive.%20He%20revealed%20that%20the%20LSG%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20the%20pacer%20to%20%26quot%3Battack%20a%20bit%26quot%3B%20and%20use%20bouncers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGreen's%20wicket%20was%20special%20because%20I%20personally%20like%20just%20like%20one%20kind%20of%20wicket%2C%20which%20is%20bowling%20people%20out%2C%20like%20any%20fast%20bowler.%20That%20over%20was%20a%20bit%20aggressive%20because%20I'd%20picked%20a%20wicket%20in%20the%20previous%20over.%20The%20captain%20also%20told%20me%20to%20attack%20a%20bit%20and%20use%20the%20bouncer%20with%20my%20pace%2C%26quot%3B%20Mayank%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20his%20side's%20plan%20was%20to%20bowl%20at%20the%20stumps%20and%20not%20to%20give%20any%20room%20to%20the%20RCB%20batters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20extra%20training%2C%20I%20just%20do%20things%20that%20make%20me%20quicker%20and%20stronger.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20played%20on%20this%20ground.%20I'd%20heard%20that%20180%20is%20easily%20chaseable%20on%20this%20ground%20but%20our%20plan%20was%20to%20keep%20bowling%20at%20the%20stumps%20and%20not%20give%20the%20batters%20any%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20match%20against%20RCB%2C%20Yadav%20bagged%20three%20wickets%20in%20his%20four-over%20spell%2C%20giving%20only%2014%20runs.%20Following%20his%20remarkable%20spell%2C%20the%20pacer%20was%20named%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'.%20The%20LSG%20seamer%20scripted%20history%20at%20the%20age%20of%2021%20as%20he%20became%20the%20first%20bowler%20in%20the%20history%20of%20IPL%20to%20win%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20award%20in%20their%20first%20two%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20ANI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712147940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fuedrsfuo_sa_625x300_03_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fmayank-yadav-or-gerald-coetzee-controversy-over-ipl-2024s-fastest-ball-explained-5367163%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants'%20IPL%202024%20match%20against%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mayank%20Yadav%20claimed%20the%20distinction%20of%20bowling%20the%20fastest%20delivery%20of%20this%20year's%20competition%20at%20156.7%20kmph.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Finnish%20school%20shooting%20motivated%20by%20bullying%20-%20police%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712147617000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FFFCE%2Fproduction%2F_133068456_07671c1affd4cac0391c2026ab81dcab89e81bf50_0_5120_34131000x667.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68720973%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20suspect%20is%20accused%20of%20killing%20a%20boy%20aged%2012%20and%20wounding%20two%20girls%20in%20Vantaa.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A78%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68720973%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc