%20noted%20that%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20students%20registered%20in%20the%20Computer%20Science%20and%20Engineering%20branch%2C%20typically%20highly%20sought-after%2C%20did%20not%20achieve%20full%20placement%20among%20those%20enrolled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20placement%20process%20at%20IIT%20Bombay%20is%20currently%20in%20progress%20and%20will%20continue%20until%20May%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20witnessed%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20percentage%20of%20students%20without%20placements%2C%20with%2035.8%20per%20cent%20remaining%20unplaced%2C%20marking%20a%202.8%20percentage%20point%20increase%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20session.%20In%202023%2C%20out%20of%20the%202%2C209%20students%20registered%20at%20IIT%20Bombay%2C%201%2C485%20had%20secured%20jobs%2C%20leaving%2032.8%20per%20cent%20unplaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20number%20of%20the%20380%20companies%20that%20participated%20in%20the%20placement%20drive%20were%20domestic%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20usual%20trend%20of%20more%20international%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20reports%20surfaced%20that%2085%20students%20at%20IIT%20Bombay%20received%20job%20offers%20with%20annual%20packages%20worth%20Rs%201%20crore.%20Later%2C%20the%20institute%20issued%20a%20clarification%20stating%20that%20only%2022%20students%20had%20received%20packages%20worth%20Rs%201%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20phase-I%20placements%20(December%201-20%2C%202023)%20incorrectly%20reported%20the%20number%20of%20accepted%20Rs%201%20crore%20plus%20offers%20as%2085.%20The%20correct%20number%20of%20accepted%20one%20crore%20plus%20offers%20is%2022.%20All%20other%20data%20reported%20is%20confirmed%20to%20be%20correct.%20The%20Placement%20Office%20of%20IIT%20Bombay%20strongly%20regrets%20this%20mistake%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20statement%20read%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712147040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-07%2Fiit-bombay_650x400_41499153428.jpg%