C%20Jen%20Glantz.%3Cp%3EJen%20Glantz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20our%20insurance%20policies%20split%20between%20us%2C%20which%20may%20be%20costing%20us%20extra.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBy%20bundling%20our%20policies%20under%20one%20company%2C%20we%20could%20get%20discounts%20on%20each%20policy.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt's%20important%20to%20check%20that%20an%20insurance%20policy%20won't%20become%20a%20bad%20deal%20after%20a%20new%20customer%20discount%20ends.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20keep%20most%20of%20our%20finances%20separate.%20We've%20been%20married%20for%20three%20years%20and%20other%20than%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-open-a-joint-credit-card%5C%22%3Ejoint%20credit%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20savings%20account%2C%20our%20money%20isn't%20commingled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20lately%2C%20as%20we've%20both%20been%20auditing%20our%20finances%2C%20we've%20realized%20that%20we're%20spending%20too%20much%20money%20on%20a%20variety%20of%20insurance%20policies%20that%20we%20each%20have.%20Between%20the%20both%20of%20us%2C%20we%20have%20renters%2C%20auto%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-pet-insurance%5C%22%3Epet%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20personal%20valuables%20insurance%20policies.%20We're%20paying%20around%20%24500%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20save%20more%20money%20this%20year%2C%20while%20not%20cutting%20back%20on%20any%20of%20our%20insurance%20policies%2C%20I%20wondered%20if%20there%20was%20a%20way%20that%20we%20could%20bundle%20these%20policies%20to%20save%20money.%20I%20spoke%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Falison-jones-b3554718%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlison%20Jones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20insurance%20agent%20with%20State%20Farm%2C%20to%20hear%20more%20about%20what%20my%20options%20are.%20Here%20are%20three%20steps%20she%20advised%20me%20to%20take%20so%20that%20I%20can%20save%20money%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBundling%20policies%20helps%20you%20earn%20a%20discount%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20mistakes%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20made%20with%20our%20insurance%20policies%20was%20not%20considering%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20we'd%20save%20if%20we%20bundled%20them%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBundling%20insurance%20is%20quite%20simple%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20shared.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20when%20a%20person%20groups%20more%20than%20one%20policy%20together.%20Not%20only%20does%20this%20give%20them%20added%20protection%20but%20it%20also%20saves%20them%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20took%20out%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-cheap-car-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Eauto%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20policy%20and%20pet%20insurance%20policy%20on%20his%20own.%20I%20took%20out%20the%20renters'%20insurance%20and%20personal%20items%20insurance%20on%20my%20own.%20Because%20of%20how%20we%20took%20these%20policies%20out%2C%20we%20didn't%20benefit%20from%20discounts%20available%20through%20the%20art%20of%20bundling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20shared%20that%20as%20an%20example%2C%20if%20a%20person%20has%20auto%20insurance%20at%20one%20insurance%20company%2C%20they%20could%20get%20a%205%25%20discount%20if%20they%20add%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-renters-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Erenters%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20that%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20discounts%20often%20reach%20up%20to%2025%25%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMoving%20all%20of%20our%20insurance%20policies%20under%20one%20roof%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20listed%20off%20the%20different%20insurance%20policies%20I%20have%2C%20Jones%20asked%20me%20if%20they%20are%20all%20under%20the%20same%20insurance%20company.%20I%20told%20her%20that%20they%20are%20not.%20We%20use%20a%20different%20company%20for%20each%20of%20our%20policies%20(auto%2C%20renters%2C%20pet%2C%20and%20jewelry).%20She%20shared%20that%20when%20you%20move%20these%20policies%20under%20one%20roof%2C%20at%20one%20insurance%20company%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20save%20money%20automatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20will%20automatically%20save%20money%20because%20you%20will%20receive%20the%20multi-line%20discount%20(also%20known%20as%20a%20bundle%20discount)%20for%20having%20more%20than%20one%20policy%20with%20the%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20this%20out%2C%20I%20called%20up%20two%20different%20insurance%20companies%20and%20asked%20each%20one%20to%20quote%20me%20on%20how%20much%20it%20would%20cost%20if%20I%20moved%20all%20of%20my%20individual%20insurance%20policies%20to%20their%20company.%20The%20companies%20were%20each%20able%20to%20give%20me%20a%20bundle%20discount%20that%20would%20save%20me%20around%2010%25%20to%2020%25%20a%20year%2C%20which%20would%20save%20me%20%24500-%241%2C000%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20also%20explained%20that%20unlike%20other%20businesses%2C%20like%20cable%20or%20phone%20services%2C%20insurance%20agents%20don't%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20negotiate%20policy%20rates%20with%20you%20or%20provide%20extra%20discounts%20and%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInsurance%20companies%20work%20differently%20than%20other%20industries%20in%20how%20prices%20are%20set%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%20%26quot%3BRates%20are%20determined%20based%20on%20hundreds%20of%20different%20factors%2C%20like%20loss%20frequency%2C%20driving%20history%2C%20credit%20characteristics%2C%20and%20longevity%20with%20prior%20carriers%2C%20and%20an%20algorithm%20is%20used%20to%20calculate%20rates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20said%20that%20the%20longer%20you%20stay%20at%20one%20insurance%20company%2C%20the%20more%20longevity%20discounts%20you%20may%20earn%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20company.%20Insurance%20carriers%20look%20at%20time%20with%20prior%20carriers%20as%20a%20positive%2C%20and%20that%20is%20part%20of%20the%20algorithm.%20She%20said%20if%20you%20do%20decide%20to%20shop%20around%20for%20plans%20elsewhere%2C%20make%20sure%20you%20go%20with%20a%20reputable%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20check%20if%20a%20company%20is%20reputable%2C%20you%20can%20look%20them%20up%20on%20one%20of%20the%20rating%20agencies%20like%20Moody's%2C%20A.M.%20Best%2C%20Fitch%2C%20and%20Standard%20%26amp%3B%20Poor%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%26quot%3BIf%20the%20deal%20seems%20too%20good%20to%20be%20true%2C%20make%20sure%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20new%20customer%20discount%20that%20will%20fall%20off%20after%20the%20first%20renewal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELife%20insurance%20can%20be%20bundled%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20current%20needs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20told%20Jones%20that%20another%20thing%20on%20my%20list%20to%20do%20this%20year%20was%20get%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-life-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Elife%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20mentioned%20that%20a%20policy%20like%20that%20could%20be%20added%20to%20my%20bundle%20and%20help%20me%20save%20more%20across%20all%20of%20my%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20goes%20back%20to%20the%20multi-line%20discount.%20Getting%20a%20life%20insurance%20policy%20will%20give%20you%20a%20multi-line%20discount%20on%20your%20auto%20insurance%2C%20and%20you%20will%20be%20better%20protected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20made%20me%20realize%20the%20importance%20of%20finding%20an%20insurance%20company%20that%20offers%20multiple%20lines%20of%20insurance%20for%20different%20life%20touchpoints%2C%20from%20property%20to%20pets%2C%20auto%2C%20and%20even%20life%20insurance.%20That%20way%2C%20I%20can%20price%20out%20a%20bundle%20for%20all%20my%20insurance%20needs%20under%20one%20roof%20and%20save%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20a%20year%20doing%20it%20this%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsurance-agent-saving-money-bundling-insurance-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712146081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66072be11caec1275a6b17ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsurance-agent-saving-money-bundling-insurance-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20insurance%20policies%20spread%20out%20across%20several%20companies%2C%20but%20if%20we%20combined%20our%20policies%20under%20one%20roof%2C%20we%20could%20save%20money.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jen%20Glantz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsurance-agent-saving-money-bundling-insurance-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taylor%20Swift%2C%20Magic%20Johnson%2C%20and%20Sam%20Altman%20made%20Forbes'%20billionaires%20list%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Here%20are%20the%20newcomers%20to%20know.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22taylor%20swift%20eras%20tour%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660d33893f923f7dab03fb64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENew%20additions%20to%20Forbes'%20billionaire%20list%20include%20Taylor%20Swift%20and%20Christian%20Louboutin.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Mazur%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETaylor%20Swift%2C%20Magic%20Johnson%2C%20and%20Sam%20Altman%20are%20among%20the%20new%20additions%20to%20Forbes'%20billionaire%20list.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESwift's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Eras%20Tour%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson's%20business%20deals%2C%20and%20Altman's%20startup%20bets%20have%20paid%20off%20hugely.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAMD's%20Lisa%20