he%20made.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20MP%20of%20both%20the%20House%20of%20Parliament%2C%20Mr%20Nirupam%20has%20been%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20party%20ever%20since%20it%20named%20its%20candidates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Is%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%20Upset%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bone%20of%20contention%20is%20the%20Mumbai%20North-West%20seat%20-%20Mr%20Nirupam%20wants%20to%20contest%20the%20seat%2C%20but%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20party%20has%20announced%20Amol%20Kirtikar%20as%20its%20candidate.%20The%20seat%20is%20currently%20held%20by%20Shiv%20Sena's%20Gajanan%20Kirtikar%2C%20who%20defeated%20Mr%20Nirupam%20in%20the%202019%20election.%20Gajanan%20Kirtikar%20sided%20with%20Eknath%20Shinde%20after%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20split.%20In%20a%20sharp%20move%2C%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20party%20fielded%20his%20son%20Amol%20from%20the%20seat.%20Gajanan%20Kirtikar%20has%20now%20said%20that%20he%20would%20not%20contest%20against%20his%20son.%20The%20BJP%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20wants%20to%20field%20its%20candidate%20there%20as%20part%20of%20its%20seat-sharing%20understanding%20with%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVerbal%20Attacks%20On%20Ally%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nirupam%20has%20said%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20should%20not%20allow%20itself%20to%20be%20arm-twisted%20by%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20party.%20Soon%20after%20the%20Sena%20list%20was%20out%2C%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20should%20not%20come%20under%20the%20threat%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20as%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20party%20is%20not%20capable%20of%20winning%20any%20seat%20without%20Congress%20support.%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20arm-twisted%20the%20Congress%20to%20take%20five%20of%20the%20six%20seats%20in%20Mumbai.%20But%20the%20Congress%20should%20not%20allow%20itself%20to%20be%20arm-twisted%20like%20this.%20This%20action%20is%20against%20the%20Congress%20and%20it's%20a%20ploy%20to%20finish%20off%20the%20party%20in%20the%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nirupam%20also%20alleged%20that%20Sena's%20candidate%20Amol%20Kirtikar%20took%20bribes%20during%20a%20free%20food%20initiative%20for%20migrant%20labourers%20during%20Covid%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Khichdi%20Scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20personal%20attack%20on%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bbachi%20khuchi%20Shiv%20Sena%20pramukh%26quot%3B%2C%20taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20split%20in%20his%20party%20after%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20mutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%20Switching%20Parties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nirupam%20has%20dropped%20broad%20hints%20over%20his%20next%20step.%20Last%20week%2C%20the%20former%20Mumbai%20Congress%20chief%20said%20he%20is%20waiting%20for%20the%20high%20command%20to%20take%20a%20decision%20over%20the%20issues%20he%20has%20raised%20and%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20options%20are%20open%20for%20me%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20BJP%20president%20Chandrashekhar%20Bawankule%20has%20said%20that%20people%20like%20Mr%20Nirupam%20are%20%26quot%3Balways%20welcome%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20party%20if%20he%20is%20ready%20and%20his%20thoughts%20align%20with%20the%20BJP.%20%26quot%3BSeeing%20the%20political%20tenure%20of%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%2C%20he%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20for%20connecting%20people%20with%20Congress.%20He%20is%20well-recognised%20in%20North%20India.%20Talks%20with%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%20have%20not%20happened%20yet%2C%20but%20if%20he%20is%20ready%20and%20his%20thoughts%20align%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20then%20people%20like%20him%20are%20always%20welcome%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20not%20alone.%20The%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Sena%20has%20also%20sent%20out%20feelers.%20Sena%20MLA%20Sanjay%20Shirsa