ource%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC5RpAKVh85c%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20mayank%20yadav%20(%40mayankyadav_8)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LSG%20seamer%20scripted%20history%20at%20the%20age%20of%2021%20as%20he%20became%20the%20first%20bowler%20in%20the%20history%20of%20IPL%20to%20win%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20award%20in%20their%20first%20two%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20clocked%20156.7%20kmph%20during%20the%20game%20against%20RCB%20and%20bowled%20the%20fastest%20delivery%20in%20the%20ongoing%20edition%20and%20overall%20the%20fourth%20fastest%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20entire%20tournament%2C%20breaking%20his%20own%20record%20made%20during%20the%20Punjab%20Kings%20match%20which%20was%20his%20debut%2C%20where%20he%20clocked%20155.8%20kmph.%20During%20his%20debut%20game%2C%20he%20took%203%2F27%20in%20four%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20just%20Mayank's%20pace%20that%20has%20many%20terming%20him%20as%20the%20next%20big%20Indian%20pace%20prospect%2C%20it%20is%20also%20the%20control%20over%20his%20line%20and%20length%20and%20intimidation%20that%20he%20has%20produced%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20couple%20of%20matches%20which%20stands%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20consecutive%20three-wicket%20hauls%20in%20his%20first%20two%20games%20also%20helped%20him%20enter%20the%20elite%20list%20of%20players.%20Yadav%20became%20the%20sixth%20bowler%20to%20scalp%20three-plus%20wicket%20hauls%20in%20each%20of%20their%20first%20two%20IPL%20matches.%20The%2021-year-old%20pacer%20now%20has%20embarked%20his%20name%20along%20with%20Lasith%20Malinga%2C%20Amit%20Singh%2C%20Mayank%20Markande%2C%20and%20Jofra%20Archer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20RCB%20elected%20to%20field%20first%20after%20winning%20the%20toss.%20Openers%20Quinton%20de%20Kock%20and%20skipper%20KL%20Rahul%20(20%20in%2014%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20sixes)%20gave%20LSG%20a%20measured%20start%20with%20a%2053-run%20opening%20stand.%20There%20was%20a%2056-run%20stand%20between%20Kock%20and%20Marcus%20Stoinis%20(24%20in%2015%20balls%2C%20with%20a%20four%20and%20two%20sixes)%20which%20helped%20LSG%20cross%20the%20100-run%20mark.%20RCB%20bowlers%20did%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20batting%20towards%20the%20end%2C%20but%20Nicholas%20Pooran%20(40*%20in%2021%20balls%2C%20with%20a%20four%20and%20five%20sixes)%20finished%20off%20well%20for%20LSG%2C%20taking%20them%20to%20181%2F5%20in%20their%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlenn%20Maxwell%20(2%2F23)%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20RCB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Siraj%2C%20Yash%20Dayal%20and%20Reece%20Topley%20took%20a%20wicket%20each%20for%20RCB.%20In%20the%20run%20chase%2C%20openers%20Virat%20Kohli%20(22%20in%2016%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20and%20Faf%20Du%20Plessis%20(19%20in%2013%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours)%20started%20off%20with%20a%2040-run%20opening%20stand.%20But%20a%20game-changing%20spell%20from%20Mayank%20Yadav%20(3%2F14)%20put%20RCB%20on%20the%20backfoot%2C%20reducing%20them%20to%2094%2F5.%20Mahipal%20Lomror%20(33%20in%2013%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%20and%20Rajat%20Patidar%20(29%20in%2021%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20tried%20to%20put%20up%20a%20fi