%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F427-michael-vaughan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMichael%20Vaughan%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20spoke%20about%20the%20topic%20and%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bstaggering%26quot%3B%20to%20see%20the%20cricket-crazy%20Indian%20fanbase%20booing%20one%20of%20their%20own%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20big%20debate%20is%20whether%20Rohit%20Sharma%20will%20end%20up%20back%20as%20captain.%20That%20has%20caused%20a%20lot%20of%20drama%20here%20in%20India.%20The%20booing%E2%80%A6%20I%20have%20to%20say%2C%20the%20Indian%20crowd%20just%20loves%20cricket.%20I%20have%20never%20heard%20them%20boo.%20I've%20certainly%20never%20heard%20them%20boo%20one%20of%20their%20own.%20I%20get%20the%20booing%20when%20he%20played%20at%20(Ahmedabad)%20against%20the%20Gujarat%20Titans.%20He's%20left%20them%20and%20joined%20Mumbai.%20He%20took%20them%20to%20a%20title.%20So%20I%20get%20that%20in%20a%20pantomime%20kind%20of%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20for%20him%20to%20go%20to%20Hyderabad%20and%20get%20booed%20and%20then%20come%20to%20Wankhede%20and%20get%20booed%20by%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20fans%20while%20he%20is%20playing%20for%20them%2C%20I'm%20staggered%20by%20it.%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20the%20Indian%20crowd%20boo%20one%20of%20their%20own.%20It's%20remarkable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaughan%20said%20on%20the%20Club%20Prairie%20Fire%20podcast%20with%20former%20Australia%20wicketkeeper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Adam%20Gilchrist%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F201-adam-gilchrist-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAdam%20Gilchrist%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Gilchrist%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20controversy%20and%20reactions%20from%20the%20fans%20points%20towards%20Rohit's%20popularity%20and%20support%20among%20the%20fanbase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20shows%20you%20the%20status%20that%20Rohit%20Sharma%20has%20in%20the%20game%20there.%20The%20mysterious%20manner%20with%20which%20it%20all%20played%20out%20initially%2C%20the%20pace%20with%20which%20it%20happened%2C%20everyone%20was%20stunned%20with%20Mumbai%20getting%20Hardik%20Pandya%20away%20from%20Gujarat%20and%20then%20Rohit%20relinquishing%20captaincy.%20It's%20an%20odd%20one.%20But%20this%20is%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20beast%20in%20the%20IPL.%20The%20tribalism%20and%20intensity%20within%20fan%20bases.%20It's%20hard%20to%20replicate%20anywhere%20else%20with%20that%20level%20of%20intensity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gilchrist%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712139780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F9g3o2jt_hardik-pandya-_640x480_02_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fim-staggered-england-greats-bombastic-take-on-ipl-crowd-booing-hardik-pandya-5366264%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20appointment%20of%20Hardik%20Pandya%20as%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20skipper%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202024%20resulted%20in%20a%20massive%20controversy%20both%20among%20experts%20as%20well%20as%20fans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22HCLTech%20announces%20alliance%20with%20Google%20Cloud%20to%20scale%20Gemini%20to%20global%20cos%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712139670000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-02%2F09%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1707457395-7328.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhcltech-announces-alliance-with-google-cloud-to-scale-gemini-to-global-cos-124040300625_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22HCLTech%20will%20familiarise%20and%20train%20its%2025%2C000%20engineers%20on%20Gemini%20for%20Google%20Cloud%20to%20help%20mutual%20clients%20innovate%20and%20optimise%20their%20businesses%20with%20GenAI%20(generative%20AI)%2C%20according%20