r%20Nikhil%20points%20out%20that%20owing%20to%20poor%20health%20services%2C%20diagnosis%20of%20abnormalities%20in%20the%20foetus%20of%20rural%20women%20is%20delayed.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20rural%20areas%2C%20women%20have%20to%20take%20a%20bus%20to%20reach%20the%20nearest%20taluk-level%20government%20hospitals%20for%20check%20ups.%20Owing%20to%20poor%20services%2C%20it%20remains%20uncertain%20whether%20the%20sonography%20will%20be%20performed%20on%20these%20patients%20on%20that%20given%20day.%20By%20the%20time%20it%E2%80%99s%20done%20for%20any%20abnormalities%20to%20be%20detected%2C%20it%20is%20too%20late%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Nikhil%20points%20out%20that%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20if%20the%20woman%20is%20forced%20to%20give%20birth%2C%20she%20is%20made%20to%20take%20the%20penalty%20for%20those%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%2C%20there%20are%20cases%20where%20women%20in%20their%20late%2040s%20miss%20out%20on%20menstruation%2C%20and%20they%20are%20advised%20to%20not%20worry%20as%20they%20are%20getting%20closer%20to%20menopause.%20One%20fine%20day%2C%20they%20find%20out%20that%20they%20are%20already%2022%20weeks%20pregnant%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F62683%2Fabortion-laws-india-supreme-court-rape-survivor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterminating%20pregnancies%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebeyond%2020%20weeks%20a%20criminal%20offence%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20gone%20through%20the%20MTP%20Act%20multiple%20times%20and%20thoroughly%20researched%20the%20topic%20only%20to%20find%20out%20that%20the%20set%20limit%20was%20arbitrary.%20There%20was%20no%20reason%20to%20support%20why%20it%20was%20set%20to%2020%20weeks%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Nikhil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20if%20a%20woman%20is%2019%20weeks%20pregnant%2C%2