%80%99t%20change.%20One%20of%20the%20three%20founding%20partners%20of%20the%20business%20continued%20to%20supervise%20each%20stage%20of%20production%20to%20ensure%20product%20quality%20didn%E2%80%99t%20wane.%20What%20also%20helped%20was%20Bharat%20joining%20the%20business%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWitnessing%20great%20promise%20in%20the%20venture%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20profession%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20in%20the%20US%20to%20join%20Adukale.%20As%20someone%20passionate%20about%20food%20and%20the%20culinary%20landscape%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20bring%20in%20my%20global%20experience%20and%20innovation%20to%20scale%20the%20brand%20and%20make%20strides%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F235046%2Fbengaluru-woman-spices-entrepreneur-coffee-sambar-powder-natural-traditional-recipes-small-biz-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebringing%20regional%20food%20to%20the%20global%20map%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20an%20Adukale%20outlet%20in%20Old%20Bengaluru%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.co