F322885%2Fkarnataka-shivaranjini-started-suggi-oota-south-indian-restaurant-in-california%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshowcasing%20the%20rich%20heritage%20of%20Karnataka%20cuisine%20to%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20delicious%20product%20at%20a%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20range%20of%20products%20currently%20comprises%20RTE%20foods%20like%20%3Cem%3Epoha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eupma%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Egojjavalakki%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebisi%20bele%20bath%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20spicy%2C%20rice-based%20dish)%2C%20blended%20spices%20like%3Cem%3E%20chutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20powders%2C%20%3Cem%3Esambar%20%3C%2Fem%3Epowder%2C%20%3Cem%3Etarkaari%20gojjina%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%20(spice%20mix%20to%20prepare%20%3Cem%3Egojju%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Enamkeens%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20savouries%20like%20%3Cem%3Enippattu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(crispy%20deep%20fried%20rice%20crackers)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekayi%20kodubale%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20popular%20deep-fried%20snack%20from%20Karnataka%20made%20using%20rice%20flour%2C%20coconut%2C%20ground%20roasted%20gram%20powder).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bharat%2C%20these%20products%20are%20free%20of%20preservatives%20and%20artificial%20colours.%20Also%2C%20with%20millets%20making%20a%20comeback%20in%20Indian%20households%20as%20superfoods%2C%20Adukale%20has%20also%20launched%20millet-based%20RTC%20products%20like%20the%20%E2%80%98Instant%20Millets%20Dose%20%5BDosa%5D%20Mix%E2%80%99%2C%20amongst%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-Old-Bangalore-1710946322.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20another%20Adukale%20outlet%20in%20Bengaluru.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-Old-Bangalore-1710946322.jpg%201200w%2C%20h