80%9CVisits%20to%20her%20home%20were%20my%20favourite%20part.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20unaware%20of%20how%20her%20deeply%20traditional%20and%20nature-friendly%20home%20would%20one%20day%20become%20an%20inspiration%20for%20my%20dream%20home%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHer%20home%20was%20very%20simple%20with%20minimal%20use%20of%20cement%20and%20very%20traditional%20in%20design%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20living%20in%20the%20city%2C%20he%20longed%20for%20a%20more%20secluded%20place%20surrounded%20by%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20saw%20the%20village%20and%20the%20piece%20of%20land%20which%20now%20holds%20my%20home%2C%20it%20was%20like%20love%20at%20first%20sight.%20I%20could%20envision%20the%20future%20of%20the%20place%20and%20hence%20chose%20to%20buy%20the%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajchandar%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20very%20interesting%20story%20that%20goes%20around%20about%20the%20hills%20surrounding%20the%20area.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20when%20Lord%20Hanuman%20lifted%20the%20Dronagiri%20Parvat%20to%20take%20it%20to%20Lord%20Lakshman%2C%20a%20piece%20of%20it%20broke%20off%20and%20fell%20here.%20Hence%2C%20these%20hills%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20medicinal%20plants%20growing%20around.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20did%20not%20want%20to%20disturb%20the%20biodiversity%20of%20the%20area%20and%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20home%20that%20blends%20into%20nature%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20they%20started%20to%20work%20on%20their%20dream%20home%20and%20opened%20their%20doors%20to%20the%20guests%20in%202022.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20decided%20to%20share%20our%20space%20with%20guests%2C%20we%20have%20hosted%20more%20than%20200%20guests%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMade%20with%20some%20mud%20and%20lots%20of%20love!%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20different%20architectures%2C%20combining%20a%20blend%20of%20Tamil%2C%20Venad%2C%20and%20Chettinad%20styles%20that%20showcase%20the%20rich%20cultural%20heritage%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20personally%20a%20collector%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F309562%2Fancient-family-collectibles-in-pictures-antique-artefacts-projectors-cameras-stamps-coins%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elove%20collecting%20artefacts%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20area.%20I%20had%20been%20collecting%20a%20lot%20of%20art%20pieces%20and%20decided%20to%20display%20them%20in%20the%20home.%20Some%20of%20these%20pieces%20are%20more%20than%20100%20years%20old%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20Rajchandar%20was%20clear%20about%20from%20the%20beginning%20is%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20use%20natural%20materials%20to%20build%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC266EwRIPRB%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC266EwRIPRB%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%